<body class="text-left">
    <div class="app-admin-wrap layout-sidebar-large">
        <div class="main-header">
            <div class="logo">
                <img src="~/nepadstaff2/dist-assets/images/logo.png" alt="">
            </div>
            <div class="menu-toggle">
                <div></div>
                <div></div>
                <div></div>
            </div>
            <div class="d-flex align-items-center">
                <!-- Mega menu -->
                <div class="dropdown mega-menu d-none d-md-block">
                    <a href="#" class="btn text-muted dropdown-toggle mr-3" id="dropdownMegaMenuButton" data-toggle="dropdown" aria-haspopup="true" aria-expanded="false">AUDA-NEPAD Integrated Planning System</a>
                    <div class="dropdown-menu text-left" aria-labelledby="dropdownMenuButton">
                        <div class="row m-0">
                            <div class="col-md-4 p-4 bg-img">
                                <h2 class="title">AUDA-NEPAD Integrated Planning System</h2>
                                <p>This is an integrated data platform for planning and reporting AUDA-NEPAD’s delivering on its mandate and strategic plan.  
                                    The goal of the strategic plan is to accelerate the integration of African economies, improve development 
                                    results and ultimately deliver enhanced quality of life for all Africans. The system unifies the assessment of AUDA-NEPAD programmatic performance by providing the tools and 
                                    instruments for capturing, monitoring and assessing the extent to which project/programme results are contributing to strategic priorities.
                                </p>
                                @* <p class="mb-4">Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet consectetur, adipisicing elit. Exercitationem odio amet eos dolore suscipit placeat.</p> *@
                                <button class="btn btn-lg btn-rounded btn-outline-warning">Learn More</button>
                            </div>
